Wu Wei.

866
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:08,600
Do you think there's a place for you

867
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,130
in the flight control hall?

868
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,720
Should I get you a standing ticket,

869
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:14,320
or a folding stool?

870
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,600
Mr. Zhao, it's a misunderstanding.

871
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:18,760
I just thought

872
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:21,120
since there's a mission right after I came,

873
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:22,440
I could go and learn.

874
00:41:24,160 --> 00:41:26,160
Don't call me that.

875
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,620
I haven't accepted you as my apprentice yet.

876
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,400
Learn?

877
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,130
What are you going to learn?

878
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:44,000
Wu Wei,

879
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,080
do you think

880
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:48,960
watching one mission

881
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:52,090
makes you an aerospace worker?

882
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:54,680
Do you think sitting in the flight control hall

883
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:56,480
makes you the chief dispatcher?

884
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,200
I asked you back then.

885
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:07,560
I asked if you were willing

886
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:08,890
to work in the archives.

887
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:10,520
You said you were.

888
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:12,160
As long as you could work here,

889
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:13,960
you were willing to do anything.

890
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:16,180
Good grief, it's only been a few days.

891
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:18,450
You haven't done anything yet,

892
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,380
and you're already scheming.

893
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:23,140
You're using this place as a stepping stone.

894
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:27,200
You're guarding such a huge archive

895
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:28,600
with so much data,

896
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:31,400
and you still think this place is too small for you?

897
00:42:32,520 --> 00:42:33,480
Mr. Zhao.

898
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:35,240
That's not what I meant.

899
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,770
I don't care what you meant.

900
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,760
If this is your attitude,

901
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,920
you'd better leave as soon as possible.

902
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,120
I won't keep you here.

903
00:42:48,560 --> 00:42:49,320
Mr. Zhao,

904
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:52,320
please assign the work for this afternoon.

905
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:55,600
Follow me.
